info.author: James Groeneveld
info.name: prompt-poet
info.summary: A powerful tool that streamlines and simplifies prompt design for both developers and non-technical users. Using a mix of YAML and Jinja2, Prompt Poet allows for flexible, dynamic prompt creation, enhancing the efficiency and quality of interactions with AI models.
